nodes.text: Yeast-worm jelly was one of the thousands of foods served at the luxurious Canto Casino Hotel on the planet Cantonica. While staying at the Canto Casino Hotel in 34 ABY, Kedpin Shoklop, a Wermal male from Werma Lesser, was served yeast-worm jelly. Knowing it was the most delicious thing he had ever tasted, he nearly cried.
Yeast-worm jelly first appeared in "Rules of the Game," a short story written by Saladin Ahmed and published by Del Rey in the book Canto Bight in 2017.
